This section contains notes and hints specific to install xajaxGrid.

1.- tar xzvf xajaxGrid-1.0.tar.gz
2.- mv xajaxGrid /WWW_PUBLIC_PATH
3.- cd /WWW_PUBLIC_PATH/xajaxGrid
4.- Create database example P.E:
	mysql -u root -p -e "CREATE DATABASE xajaxGrid"
5.- Upload data
	mysql xajaxGrid -u root -p < sql/xajaxGrid.sql
6.- Edit and change the line 13 by db parameters P.E.
	define('SQLC', "mysql://User:Password@localhost/DataBaseName"); 
7.- Show your URL, P.E: http://mydomain.com/xajaxGrid/

If you have any problem, please send me a email to jjvema@yahoo.com.

Jesus Velazquez
